Package: rSCOPE
Type: Package
Title: Run SCOPE model through R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alby Duarte Rocha
Authors@R: person("Alby", "Duarte Rocha", email = "a.duarterocha@tu-berlin.de", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6370-1240"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <a.duarterocha@tu-berlin.de>
Description: This package compile function to: 1) prepare inputs parameters for modelling with SCOPE, including download DWD data, Berlin Environmental Atlas, and LAI copernicus, interpolate to a grid for multiple timestamps; 2) clean Eddy covariance flux data; 3) extract surface properties using footprint modelling; 4) run SCOPE using, selecting the inputs parameters (variables and contants) and model setting; 5) analyse the results, checking the inputs simulated, output preditions and accuracy. 
